lead_paragraph: Hillary Clinton is expected to help raise campaign cash for Democratic Sen. Jeanne Shaheen of New Hampshire — an important place to maintain friends, should the former secretary of state choose to make a second bid for the White House.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton to Raise Money for NH's Shaheen
